\beta \left( x,n\right) =\dfrac {\left( n-1\right) !}{x\left( x+1\right) \left( x+2\right) ....\left( x+n-1\right) }
\beta \left( x,n\right) =\dfrac {\Gamma \left( x\right) \Gamma \left( n\right) }{\Gamma \left( x+n\right) }
\Gamma \left( n\right) =\left( n-1\right) !
\beta(x,n)=\int_0^1 t^{x-1}(1-t)^{n-1}dt
\beta(x,n)=(n-1)\frac1x\int_0^1 t^x(1-t)^{n-2}dt=\frac{n-1}x \beta(x+1,n-1)
